sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant R as ⚛️ React SPA
    participant V as 💚 Vue Checkout
    participant J as ☕ Java Engine
    participant P as 🐍 Python Auditor
    participant S as 💾 Storage

    rect rgb(26, 26, 46)
        Note over U,R: Phase 1 — Movie Selection
        U->>R: Browse Movies & Select Showtime
        R->>R: Load MovieDetail with Context
        U->>R: Pick Seats on Interactive Map
        R->>J: Request Mutex Seat Lock
        J-->>R: Thread-0 locks seats (5 min hold)
    end

    rect rgb(22, 33, 62)
        Note over R,J: Phase 2 — Payment & Validation
        R->>V: Mount Vue Card Checkout Form
        U->>V: Enter Card Number & Expiry
        V->>J: Validate via Luhn Algorithm
        J-->>V: ✅ Card Valid / ❌ Card Invalid
        J->>J: Track Card Object in ArrayList
        J->>S: BufferedWriter → cards.dat
    end

    rect rgb(26, 26, 46)
        Note over V,P: Phase 3 — Password Security Audit
        U->>V: Enter Password
        V->>J: Java Weak/Strong Check
        V->>P: Python Abstract Audit
        P->>P: Length + Complexity + Pattern Checks
        P-->>V: Audit Score & Vulnerability Report
        P->>P: Plot Stats via Matplotlib Canvas
    end

    rect rgb(15, 52, 96)
        Note over U,S: Phase 4 — OTP & Ticket Generation
        R->>U: Display OTP Verification Panel
        U->>R: Submit 6-Digit OTP Code
        R->>S: Save Booking to LocalStorage
        R->>U: Generate 3D Interactive Ticket
        U->>R: Click QR Code → Verify Entry
        R-->>U: ✅ Status: Verified + Timestamp
    end
